  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nI try to use a `@RoutingFilter`  to set information to a request scoped bean which I will use later e.g. during a health check. This seems to work, but only for the first call. Every consecutive call fails to propage the request scoped bean.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nEvery call should propagate request scoped information set within a `@RoutingFilter` as expected\r\n\r\n### How to Reproduce?\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/HerrDerb/quarkus-issue/tree/vertx-routes-filter-issue\r\n\r\n### Quarkus version or git rev\r\n\r\n3.2.2.Final\r\n",
